<plot>Before Neo and Morpheus became a household name and an annual Halloween costume, this Mtv original movie special was the first of it's kind paving the way for hundreds of half assed replicas. Hosted by Chris Connelly, on the actual Matrix movie set, the special delivered viewers an indepth look into the making of the Matrix, the Movie. Exclusive interviews with the cast and crew helped make this show the Ultimate guide to the Matrix and it's everlasting sound track.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?575739</url></doc>
